| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2554 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 87a4aeb0-26df-5cbd-8b5a-1ef25ef2d040"
